{"tid":1000504,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"營養師入 到底雞肉有無肌酸","createTime":"2019-01-29T12:49:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-29T22:51:19.000Z","uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"09168fe2955232c2e24fbc25d84451cab833bddd","tid":1000504,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T12:49:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://truehealth.com.tw/2017/06/creatine-weight-training/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruehealth.com.tw%2F2017%2F06%2Fcreatine-weight-training%2F&d=2pBoyAcJJfm%2FTk9I6oZxMN%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=0731fd63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://truehealth.com.tw/2017/06/creatine-weight-training/</a><br />\n<br />\n之前睇咗篇咁嘅文章<br />\n<br />\n話雞肉不含肌酸 我心諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都on9<br />\n<br />\n之後我搵資料 有人話雞肉唔係無肌酸 係比其實肉少好多 <br />\n<br />\n但我啱啱又見到張圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m4eeaxB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm4eeaxB.png&h=5b502e7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明明每kg只係比其他肉少啲 點解又話佢好少肌酸 又話佢無肌酸 點解要屈雞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bf1ac77f010122981f1543fb229325e51fd4eac","tid":1000504,"uid":199211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T15:19:46.000Z","msg":"條腰好幼 點東可以粗翻啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a98afea963b79d8d5a9773a420ed854cd8b61a6f","tid":1000504,"uid":199211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T15:19:56.000Z","msg":"點樣*"},{"pid":"89315c47c27b0ca3fa3d2f8612ee90feddee162e","ti